{"tid":584974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門田景邨老婦墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-03-08T09:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T09:03:20.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"80c0f0df30b3c2c43f5ee71c07d77e72261138fb","tid":584974,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:01:24.000Z","msg":"屯門田景邨田樂樓，早上10時許，一名年約80歲老婦由高處墮下，倒臥在一樓簷篷，昏迷不醒，保安員聽到隆然巨響發現報警，救護員接報到場，將昏迷老婦送院搶救，惜最終不治。警方調查後獲悉女事主姓譚（81歲），據悉，譚婦有身體病患。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180308/57918505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180308%2F57918505&d=XZKGZzH3RpoVKciqCDwveAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=03336545\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180308%2F57918505&h=63e6d7e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180308/57918505</a>"},{"pid":"300c31f361c2b2c469163a2e7b26479cc6283da5","tid":584974,"uid":154725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:03:20.000Z","msg":"近呢個星期好似少左跳樓<br />\n定只係報少左?"}]}